Wolves of Winter - Wolves of Winter (2016)320ak

On January 9th, 2016 Wolves of Winter released their self titled debut studio album which was produced by Josh McGee, engineered by Patrick Hogg and mastered by Jeff Harris. The album, offered both as a physical CD and digital download was well received by the  stoner rock community and gained positive reviews from popular web zines and blogs
